    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Staff weapons used both in warfare and tournaments, consisting of a long shaft with a steel head, carried by mounted knights or light cavalry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
